title: Envy Nightclub shooting: 4 shot in Palm Springs club on Forest Hill Blvd.
content:
Autoplay:XShooting at Envy Nightclub off of Forest Hill Blvd.
PALM SPRINGS, Fla. - A night of fun, turned into terror as shots rang out at a Palm Springs nightclub early Saturday morning, leaving several people injured.
Envy Nightclub on Forest Hill Rd. remained roped off Saturday morning while police determined what happened.
Police said around 2:30 this morning, shots were fired inside the club, where four victims were struck.
Police said the club was full at the time and everyone scattered once they heard the gunfire.
Victims arrived at several area medical centers to be checked out but police said, all the injuries were non-life-threatening.
There are no suspects in custody.
Palm Springs police are asking witnesses to call with information.
